alpovertyportal.org/web/guest/country/home/tags/madagascar</a></li>\n<li>World Food Program (WFP). Country Programme Madagascar 2005-2009. Text online: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.wfp.org/content/country-programme-madagascar-2005-2009\">http://www.wfp.org/content/country-programme-madagascar-2005-2009</a></li>\n<li>United Nations Development Programme. Country profile. Text online: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://hdrstats.undp.org/en/countries/profiles/MDG.html\">http://hdrstats.undp.org/en/countries/profiles/MDG.html</a></li>\n<li>United Nations Development Programme. Plan d'Action du Programme Pays/CPAP 2008-2011. Text online: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.snu.mg/new/sites/pnud/article.php?article_id=749&amp;lang=fr\">http://www.snu.mg/new/sites/pnud/article.php?article_id=749&amp;lang=fr</a></li>\n<li>Deutsche Gesellschaft f\u00fcr Internationale Zusammenarbeit web site. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.gtz.de/en/weltweit/afrika/587.htm\">http://www.gtz.de/en/weltweit/afrika/587.htm</a></li>\n<li>IFPRI Food Security Portal <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.foodsecurityportal.org/madagascar/resources\">http://www.foodsecurityportal.org/madagascar/resources</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2181\nCached time: 20180914231623\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.106 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 314/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 5011/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 223/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 1736/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.020/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 899 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclus